sub_title: Research Technician department of Molecular Biology at Radboud University
summary: In 2019, I finished the education Biology and Medical Laboratory Research. I am highly interested in immunology, molecular biology and cell biology. During my internships and my current job as a research technician I got experience in working with different molecular techniques. I describe myself as an accurate and independent worker who also likes to work in a team and masters new techniques quickly.
